{
  "dashboard": {
    "title": "⚡ RHINOMETRIC API Performance",
    "tags": ["rhinometric", "api", "performance"],
    "timezone": "browser",
    "schemaVersion": 38,
    "version": 0,
    "refresh": "5s",
    "panels": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "type": "text",
        "title": "API Performance Overview",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 0,
          "w": 24,
          "h": 3
        },
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "# ⚡ RHINOMETRIC API Performance Dashboard\n\n**Monitor all API endpoints in real-time**\n\n- 🔗 **API Connector**: Data source connection management\n- 📊 **Dashboard Builder**: Visual dashboard designer\n- 🔐 **License Server**: License validation and management\n- 📈 **Landing Page**: Platform gateway\n\n**Metrics**: Requests/s, Latency (p50/p95/p99), Error Rate, Uptime\n\n---"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "type": "row",
        "title": "🔗 API Connector Metrics",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 3,
          "w": 24,
          "h": 1
        },
        "collapsed": false
      },
      {
        "id": 3,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "API Connector Status",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 4,
          "w": 3,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "up{job=\"api-connector\"}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "mappings": [
              {
                "type": "value",
                "options": {
                  "0": {"text": "DOWN", "color": "red"},
                  "1": {"text": "UP", "color": "green"}
                }
              }
            ],
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "red"},
                {"value": 1, "color": "green"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 4,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Requests/s",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 3,
          "y": 4,
          "w": 3,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{job=\"api-connector\"}[5m]))",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "reqps",
            "decimals": 2
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 5,
        "type": "gauge",
        "title": "Latency p95",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 6,
          "y": 4,
          "w": 3,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{job=\"api-connector\"}[5m])) by (le))",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "s",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 1,
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 0.5, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 0.8, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 6,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Error Rate",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 9,
          "y": 4,
          "w": 3,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{job=\"api-connector\",status=~\"5..\"}[5m])) / sum(rate(http_requests_total{job=\"api-connector\"}[5m])) * 100",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 1, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 5, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 7,
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Request Rate",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 12,
          "y": 4,
          "w": 6,
          "h": 8
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{job=\"api-connector\"}[5m])) by (method)",
            "legendFormat": "{{method}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "reqps"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 8,
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Response Time Distribution",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 18,
          "y": 4,
          "w": 6,
          "h": 8
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{job=\"api-connector\"}[5m])) by (le))",
            "legendFormat": "p50",
            "refId": "A"
          },
          {
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{job=\"api-connector\"}[5m])) by (le))",
            "legendFormat": "p95",
            "refId": "B"
          },
          {
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{job=\"api-connector\"}[5m])) by (le))",
            "legendFormat": "p99",
            "refId": "C"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "s"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 9,
        "type": "table",
        "title": "Top Endpoints by Request Count",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 8,
          "w": 12,
          "h": 8
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "topk(10, sum by (path) (rate(http_requests_total{job=\"api-connector\"}[5m])))",
            "format": "table",
            "instant": true,
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "transformations": [
          {
            "id": "organize",
            "options": {
              "renameByName": {
                "path": "Endpoint",
                "Value": "Requests/s"
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      },
